step.action:
Read the story file frontmatter to populate a new entry:
    {story_key}:
      title: {from frontmatter title field}
      epic: {extract epic key from frontmatter epic field, e.g., "E9 — Enhanced Agent Memory" → "E9"}
      status: {new_status}
      sprint_id: {from frontmatter or sprint_id parameter}
      priority: {from frontmatter}
      risk: {from frontmatter}
      author: {from frontmatter}
      file: {story filename, e.g., "E9-S13-consolidate-dual-gaia-and-memory-directories.md"}
    Update last_updated timestamp.
